author: KEXP
description:
http://KEXP.ORG presents Des Demonas performing live in the KEXP studio. Recorded November 21, 2024.

Songs:
Obsession
Miles Davis Headwound Blues
Psychic Bloc
The South Will Never Rise Again
Conduit (Televised Crimewave)

Jacky Cougar Abok - Vocals
Mark Cisneros - Guitar
Paul Vivari - Organ, Bass Machine
Matt Gatwood - Drums

Host: Brian Foss
Audio Engineers: Kevin Suggs, Julian Martlew
Mastering: Julian Martlew
Cameras: Jim Beckmann, Carlos Cruz, Scott Holpainen & Luke Knecht
Editor: Scott Holpainen
